      "role": "user",
      "content": "it never actually stops. even when i sleep, the nerve pain is just there, like a constant electricity under my skin. i'm just so tired of fighting for a life that feels like it’s just one long, agonizing sentence. it feels like there's no point in just... enduring it anymore.",
